    emi "あらら、それはとっても残念だね、琳"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3771
translate jp a3_emi_up_down_and_up_again_f132638c:

    # emi "Could we have a little privacy now, please?"
    emi "じゃあそろそろ、二人きりにさせてもらえないかな？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3787
translate jp a3_emi_up_down_and_up_again_8195ae23:

    # "Rin shrugs, as if to say 'Can you?' and hooks her foot around the door, pulling it closed behind her."
    "琳は『いいよ？』とでもいうように肩をすくめ、ドアに足をかけると開いて出て行き、後ろ向きにドアを閉める。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3792
translate jp a3_emi_up_down_and_up_again_0f2a173e:

    # "We both dissolve into raucous laughter, unable to deal with Rin's bizarrely timed visit any other way."
    "琳の異常なまでのタイミングでの登場に耐え切れず、二人でバカみたいに大笑いを始める。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3794
translate jp a3_emi_up_down_and_up_again_d4335c11:

    # "After our laughter dies down, I look to Emi. We're both a total mess."
    "笑いが止み、俺は笑美を見つめる。二人ともひどいありさまだ。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3798
translate jp a3_emi_up_down_and_up_again_b1afde36:

    # hi "Well."
    hi "さて"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3803
translate jp a3_emi_up_down_and_up_again_3de31db1:

    # "Emi raises an eyebrow."
    "笑美が眉を上げる。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3805
translate jp a3_emi_up_down_and_up_again_9ea2d850:

    # emi "Well?"
    emi "さてさて？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3807
translate jp a3_emi_up_down_and_up_again_755b0e12:

    # hi "Again?"
    hi "もう一回？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3812
translate jp a3_emi_up_down_and_up_again_1b844624:

    # "Emi grins and laughs, and then she nods."
    "笑美は口をあけて笑い、そしてうなずく。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3817
translate jp a3_emi_up_down_and_up_again_ab45c742:

    # emi "We should probably ditch the clothes, this time."
    emi "今度はちゃんと服を脱いでからしたほうがいいかもね"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3835
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_b0a49044:

    # "The sunlight breaks through my window shortly before my alarm ruins the morning silence."
    "目覚ましが朝の静けさを打ち砕く直前になって、日差しが窓を通り抜けて差し込んでくる。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3839
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_6441d2ec:

    # "I feel sore."
    "体中が痛い。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3841
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_921e7b26:

    # "The events of the previous evening suddenly intrude upon my consciousness, and I find myself blushing."
    "前の晩の出来事が、とつぜん俺の意識のなかに押し入ってきて、赤くなっている自分に気づく。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3843
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_2938d594:

    # "That was an eventful evening - and it explains perfectly the soreness in my lower back."
    "目まぐるしい夜だった――背中の痛みの原因はまさにそれだ。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3845
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_982d5491:

    # "The walk back, as I recall, had been rather tense."
    "思い返してみるに、帰りは緊張したな。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3847
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_5e17ace9:

    # "My trousers having been… soiled, I had washed them off in the bathroom before going back to my room."
    "ズボンが……その、汚れて、部屋に戻る前にシャワー室でそれを洗っていた。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3849
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_20d625c9:

    # "But there was still a fairly obvious-looking stain on the front."
    "ところが、前の方にも明らかな汚れがついていた。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3851
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_aa1576ff:

    # "Fortunately for me, the only person I ran into on my way back was Kenji."
    "幸運なことに、戻る途中で出会ったのは健二だけだった。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3853
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_b2f85952:

    # "And he didn't notice a thing."
    "そして健二はなんにも気づいちゃいなかった。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3855
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_ea286f07:

    # "Well, apart from my being in the general vicinity."
    "まあ、俺がすぐそばにいるということ以外は。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3857
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_2d4fb63f:

    # "Of course he'd asked how the night went, and whether or not I'd learned anything of importance."
    "もちろんその夜なにをしていたかとか、何か重要なことを突き止めたかとか、そんなことは聞いてきた。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3859
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_096d69be:

    # "I don't even know if I opened my mouth to answer; I was too tired to care."
    "自分が答えるために口を開いたかさえ覚えていない。それほど疲れていたんだ。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3861
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_73e005e2:

    # "And this morning, I'll admit that I'm feeling pretty worn out."
    "そして今朝、俺は疲れ果てていることを認めざるを得ない。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3863
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_08f7aeea:

    # "Still, Emi had promised to meet me at the track, and I'd hate to disappoint."
    "それでも、笑美とは運動場で会う約束をしているし、がっかりさせたくはない。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3869
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_776a3a29:

    # "She is indeed waiting for me when I arrive."
    "笑美はまさに俺が来るのを待っている。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3871
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_720857e0:

    # "Doing her best to look cheery, despite the fact that she's sitting in a wheelchair."
    "車椅子に座っているにもかかわらず、笑美はできるだけ明るく振る舞おうとする。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3873
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_3a30e736:

    # "I wave to her and begin stretching."
    "俺は手を振って、ストレッチを始める。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3875
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_54901257:

    # hi "You're early."
    hi "早いな"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3880
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_f2c6c02e:

    # "Emi frowns and shakes her head."
    "笑美は顔をしかめて、頭を振る。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3885
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_741054c6:

    # emi "Ridiculous."
    emi "バカ言わないで"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3887
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_2301af8a:

    # emi "{b}You're{/b} late."
    emi "{b}そっちが{/b}遅いんだよ"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3892
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_7103fe05:

    # emi "Overslept, Hisao?"
    emi "寝坊したんでしょ、久夫？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3897
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_13f12191:

    # emi "All tuckered out?"
    emi "くたくたになっちゃったのかな？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3899
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_2e19cb18:

    # "Well, at least she seems more like her old self."
    "やれやれ、ようやく元の調子に戻ったみたいだ。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3901
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_6fcc4204:

    # "And as expected, she doesn't seem that shy about mentioning our… previous activities."
    "予想通り、笑美はこの前の……行為、に触れることに全く気後れする様子がない。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3903
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_fc860247:

    # hi "Hey, you're lucky I could show up at all."
    hi "なあ、俺がちゃんとここに来れて良かっただろ"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3905
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_ae6848bd:

    # hi "All that cardiovascular activity last night, I nearly thought I'd have to see the nurse afterwards."
    hi "夕べはあんなに心臓を酷使したからな、あとでナースのところに行かなきゃいけないかと思ったぐらいなんだぞ"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3910
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_7c50dbf4:

    # "Emi laughs out loud, then her face suddenly becomes concerned."
    "笑美が大声で笑うと、その顔がとつぜん心配そうな表情になる。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3917
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_6921cc44:

    # emi "Hey, that's not uh…"
    emi "ねえ、それってなんか……"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3919
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_5bfda2a6:

    # emi "I mean, you're not…"
    emi "えっとね、君って……"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3921
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_b7415c48:

    # hi "Go on, spit it out."
    hi "いいよ、言えよ"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3926
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_e036cc69:

    # emi "It's just that it would be hard to explain if you had an episode while we were…"
    emi "その……最中に発作が起きたりしたら、説明が難しいと思うんだけど"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3928
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_04be15a3:

    # hi "Oh."
    hi "ああ"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3930
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_338867b4:

    # hi "{b}Oh.{/b}"
    hi "{b}ああ{/b}"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3932
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_98cbe744:

    # "Now that she mentions it, it really is a legitimate concern."
    "言われてみれば、まさしく理にかなった心配事だ。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3934
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_0e0ad784:

    # "I certainly hadn't thought of it last night, of course - other, more pressing concerns had been at hand."
    "夕べの俺は確かにそんなこと考えもしなかった。もちろん……別の差し迫った問題があったからだ。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3936
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_0abd664d:

    # hi "Well, I don't think anything we, er, {b}do{/b} is going to be any more of a strain than these morning runs, and I handle those fine, so…"
    hi "なあ、俺たちがその、{b}ナニを{/b}するにしても、朝のランニングより負担がかかることなんてないだろうし、その程度なら俺もぜんぜん問題ないからさ……"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3941
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_71c60631:

    # "Emi considers this point."
    "笑美はその点について考える。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3946
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_e852e6ce:

    # "A devious light appears in her eyes."
    "その目に捻くれた光が宿る。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3950
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_c4648bf1:

    # emi "Say…"
    emi "あのさ……"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3952
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_34d1d59d:

    # hi "Hmm?"
    hi "うん？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3957
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_86d34890:

    # "The light vanishes, and Emi grins ruefully at me."
    "その光は消え去って、笑美は悲しげな笑みを浮かべる。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3959
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_05b9bacb:

    # "I can't help but feel vaguely suspicious."
    "なんだか怪しいという気分がしてしかたない。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3964
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_ace437d0:

    # emi "I seem to have forgotten a pair of gloves."
    emi "手袋、忘れちゃったみたい"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3966
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_6d1f773c:

    # hi "What do you need gloves for?"
    hi "手袋なんてなにに使うんだ？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3971
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_cf91a250:

    # "Emi indicates the chair upon which she is seated."
    "笑美は座っている車椅子を指し示す。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3973
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_b60d5737:

    # emi "For this, of course!"
    emi "これに決まってるじゃん！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3978
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_71da3265:

    # emi "Sure, regular moving around is all well and good without 'em, but I want to be able to get a good workout."
    emi "そりゃ、手袋なしでも普段の移動には全然問題ないけど、でもきちんと運動したいからさ"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3983
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_e977dc2f:

    # emi "And to get that kind of speed, you gotta have gloves if you don't want blisters."
    emi "そのくらいのスピードを出すとなると、手袋しなきゃ手に豆ができちゃう"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3985
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_95703a7f:

    # hi "So what, are you wussing out on me then? Do I have to go it alone?"
    hi "それがなんだよ、ビビってるのか？　俺ひとりで走れってのか？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3990
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_d22f94dc:

    # "Emi thinks for a minute - or pretends to think."
    "笑美は少しのあいだ考える――か、考えるふりをする。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3995
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_074a017f:

    # emi "Hmm… if I remember right, there's a spare pair or two in the track shed."
    emi "うーん……たしか、予備の手袋が１つか２つ体育倉庫にあったかも"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3997
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_24f5aea1:

    # "So she does seriously want to do it, then."
    "じゃあ笑美は本気で走りたいんだな。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3999
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_43394219:

    # "But in her normal school uniform? I'd have expected her to wear her gym outfit for something like this."
    "でも、普通の制服でか？　こういうことだからてっきり体操服で来ると思ってたのに。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4001
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_764f243d:

    # hi "Wait, what are they doing there?"
    hi "待った、どうしてあんなところに手袋があるんだ？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4006
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_b13bd09c:

    # "Emi looks askance at me."
    "笑美は横目で俺を見る。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4008
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_939aa7b6:

    # emi "Seriously? You can't think of why a shed full of track supplies at a school for the disabled would have racing gloves?"
    emi "本気で言ってるの？　障害児向けの学校に陸上の用具が山ほど入ってる倉庫があるのに、そこにレース用の手袋がある理由も想像ができない？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4010
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_dda2dfd1:

    # "Well, when she puts it that way, I suppose that makes perfect sense."
    "なるほど、そう言われれば完全に納得できる。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4012
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_619e3982:

    # hi "Hey, I'm still getting used to this place. Give me a break, huh?"
    hi "おい、まだこの場所には慣れきってないんだ。勘弁してくれよな"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4017
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_ec071e50:

    # emi "I guess I can let it slide this time."
    emi "ま、今回は大目に見てあげてもいいかな"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4022
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_ba2494ad:

    # emi "Now come on, I'll need your help."
    emi "じゃあ来て。手伝ってほしいんだ"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4024
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_4920876b:

    # "I can't imagine what for, but then again I didn't have a clue why racing gloves would be in the shed, so I'm not willing to press the issue."
    "なにを手伝うんだか想像がつかないけど、一方でレース用の手袋が倉庫にある理由もさっぱりわからないので、追及する気にはならない。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4029
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_1f3d2374:

    # "Emi navigates her way to the shed easily enough, though I can hear her grumbling under her breath."
    "笑美は小声でぶつくさいいながらも、俺をいとも簡単に倉庫まで案内する。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4031
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_4d69f9eb:

    # "It's actually kinda cute."
    "実際、なんだか可愛らしいな。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4033
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_96f87b13:

    # "I hurry a little to reach the door first. Opening it will be easier for me than for her."
    "俺は少し急いでドアに先にたどり着く。俺なら笑美よりも簡単に開けられるだろう。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4045
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_f5938f8a:

    # "The door opens, and Emi starts to wheel inside, only to come to a sudden halt at the doorway."
    "ドアを開いて、笑美は中に入っていくけど、戸口で突然止まる。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4047
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_b7750477:

    # "It seems the doorsill is slightly too high for her to get over by herself."
    "笑美が自分で乗り越えるには、段差がいくらか高すぎたみたいだ。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4064
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_2d52f173:

    # "She makes a few runs at it, unsuccessfully, before crossing her eyes and glaring at the offending object."
    "障害物をじっとにらみつけて、何度か助走をつけてもうまくいかない。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4069
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_c981799b:

    # emi "Stupid wheelchair."
    emi "もう、ポンコツ車椅子"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4074
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_e6123f1c:

    # emi "Hisao, can you give me a hand here?"
    emi "久夫、手伝ってくれない？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4076
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_40be391a:

    # hi "Sure, no problem."
    hi "いいよ、もちろん"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4081
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_49db032d:

    # "It's a simple enough matter for me to bump Emi over the doorway, jostling her slightly."
    "俺なら笑美を少し押して、戸口の向こうにやるのは簡単なことだ。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4086
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_993b2aea:

    # emi "Hey, easy there!"
    emi "ちょっと、気をつけてよ！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4088
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_c1b82a2f:

    # hi "Whoops! Sorry."
    hi "うわっ！　ごめん"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4090
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_b8b13aa6:

    # "It's at about this time that I fail to notice where I'm going and run Emi's chair into a mat."
    "このとき、俺は進んでいる先にマットがあることに気づかなかった。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4101
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_e29c2896:

    # "She gives a startled yelp and topples forward out of her chair."
    "笑美は驚いて声をあげると、椅子から前のめりに転げ落ちてしまう。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4103
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_213dddc2:

    # "There's a moment of silence as I gaze in horror upon what I've done, and Emi glares at me."
    "この沈黙のさなか、自分のやらかしたことを恐る恐る見届けると、笑美は俺をにらんでいた。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4105
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_d5796930:

    # emi "Hisao…"
    emi "久夫……"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4107
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_80452e63:

    # hi "Yes?"
    hi "な、なんだ？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4109
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_33ea2d78:

    # emi "Promise me you'll never work at a hospital."
    emi "絶対に病院では働かないって約束して"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4111
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_04d2e458:

    # hi "Sorry! I didn't mean to!"
    hi "ごめん！　わざとじゃないから！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4113
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_47756de2:

    # "Emi giggles, and holds up a hand."
    "笑美はくすくす笑うと、手を持ち上げる。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4115
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_f70ee8d8:

    # emi "Would you kindly help me back into my chair, Hisao?"
    emi "車椅子に戻してくださる、久夫さん？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4125
translate jp a3_emi_storage_space_efd25c7c:

    # "As I bend down to pick up Emi, she grins in triumph and pulls me into a kiss that quickly has us both entirely unconcerned about getting her back into the chair."
